497
00:16:20,233 --> 00:16:23,443
(Complying with an unreasonable request)

498
00:16:25,403 --> 00:16:27,012
My gosh. I should stand next to her.

499
00:16:27,013 --> 00:16:29,283
(Feeling bad for her, Yeon Seok walks over to her.)

500
00:16:31,943 --> 00:16:33,653
